---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Sara's OSINT Resources">
  <article class="surface p-6 sm:p-10 prose prose-invert max-w-none">
    <PageHeader title="About" />

    <section class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg">
        Greetings &mdash; My name is Sara.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm on a quest to launch my OSINT career. This site is a work in progress &mdash;
        I will be adding material to it slowly but surely. It will be to showcase what I've done
        and perhaps provide information for others looking to learn.
      </p>
      <p>
        For more information and updates, see
        <a href="https://sara-osint.blogspot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">my blog</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2>CTF Accomplishments</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 not-prose">
        <div class="surface-card p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-200">3rd Place</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-zinc-300/80">OSINT CTF</p>
        </div>
        <div class="surface-card p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-200">4th Place</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-zinc-300/80">Defcon OSINT CTF &mdash; August 2022</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6">
        At <a href="https://defcon.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Defcon's</a> OSINT CTF
        held by <a href="https://www.tracelabs.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Trace Labs</a>
        in August 2022 &mdash; our 2-person team placed 4th!
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-cyan-200">WHOHOO WALMART GREETERS!</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2>Coursework & Training</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Online Harassment: Strategies for Journalists' Defense</strong>, February 2021<br />
          Knight Center for Journalism in the Americas, Online
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Strategy & Tactics for OSINT CTFs</strong>, October 2020<br />
          Alethe Denis &mdash; Innocent Lives Foundation, Online
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Digital Investigations for Journalists</strong>, November 2020<br />
          Knight Center for Journalism in the Americas, Online
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>The Power of Digital Audio Storytelling</strong>, November 2022<br />
          Knight Center for Journalism in the Americas, Online
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Masterclass on Online Research with Paul Myers</strong>, May 2020<br />
          Global Network of Investigative Journalists (GIJN), Webinar Series: Investigating the Pandemic
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Alternative & Advanced Search Engine Intelligence (AASEI)</strong>, May 2022<br />
          Joe Gray &mdash; Antisyphon Training
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Investigative Reporting in Platforms</strong>, June 2023<br />
          How to Dig into Social Accounts, Images, Ads, and Messaging Apps, Online
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2>Volunteering</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>CTI League</strong> &mdash; November 2020 to August 2021<br />
          Threat Response/Insight, Remote/Online
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Night Owl Reconnaissance</strong> &mdash; August 2023 to Present<br />
          OSINT Investigator
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2>Community</h2>
      <div class="not-prose flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/sara.osint/resources/osint4good" class="inline-block rounded-full border border-cyan-400/30 bg-cyan-400/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-cyan-200 transition-colors hover:bg-cyan-400/20">
          #OSINT4GOOD
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.secjuice.com/social-media-intelligence-socmint/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block rounded-full border border-cyan-400/30 bg-cyan-400/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-cyan-200 transition-colors hover:bg-cyan-400/20">
          #SOCMINT
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.rusi.org/publication/osinf-lifeblood-decision-making" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block rounded-full border border-cyan-400/30 bg-cyan-400/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-cyan-200 transition-colors hover:bg-cyan-400/20">
          #OSINF
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.osint.industries/post/what-is-dark-web-intelligence-darkint-beginners-guide" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block rounded-full border border-cyan-400/30 bg-cyan-400/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-cyan-200 transition-colors hover:bg-cyan-400/20">
          #DARKINT
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions, comments, or suggestions? Reach out via the
        <a href="https://sara-osint.blogspot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">external blog</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
